Class DefaultAuthenticationSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.unicon.cas.addons.authentication.internal.DefaultAuthenticationSupport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuthenticationSupport

    public class DefaultAuthenticationSupport
extends Object
implements AuthenticationSupport
    Default implementation of AuthenticationSupport.

    Uses CAS' TicketRegistry to retrieve TGT and its associated objects by provided tgt String token

    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    Dmitriy Kopylenko, Unicon, inc.
